net.corda.core.node.services

Class Vault.Page<T extends ContractState>

  • net.corda.core.node.services.Vault.Page<T>
  • Enclosing class:
    Vault<T extends ContractState>

    public static class Vault.Page<T extends ContractState>

    Returned in queries VaultService.queryBy and VaultService.trackBy. A Page contains:

    1. a List of actual class StateAndRef requested by the specified class QueryCriteria to a maximum of MAX_PAGE_SIZE.

    2. a List of associated class Vault.StateMetadata, one per class StateAndRef result.

    3. a total number of states that met the given class QueryCriteria if a class PageSpecification was provided, otherwise it defaults to -1.

    4. Status types used in this query: StateStatus.UNCONSUMED, StateStatus.CONSUMED, StateStatus.ALL.

    5. Other results as a List of any type (eg. aggregate function results with/without group by).

    Note: currently otherResults are used only for Aggregate Functions (in which case, the states and statesMetadata results will be empty).

    See Also:
    VaultService.queryBy, VaultService.trackBy, List, class StateAndRef, class QueryCriteria, List, class Vault.StateMetadata, class StateAndRef, class QueryCriteria, class PageSpecification, List
